User Stories
1: user login page
As a user, I want to access my account, so I can find my items.
2: user registration page
As a user, I want to create an account, so I can use the app to find my items
3: user report lost item
As a user, I want to report a lost item, so I can possibly find my item
4: user report found item
As a user, I want to report that I found an item, so it can be returned to its owner
5: google map display of items
As a user, I want to see a map of the lost item, so I can retrieve my lost item
6: status of lost items
As a user, I want to see if my items were found, so I can see if I can retreive them yet
7: user can contact other users
As a user, I want to contact the person who found my item, so I can confirm it is my item and can retrieve it
8: user search for items
As a user, I want to search through the lost items, so I can identitfy if it is my lost item
9: user logout feature
As a user, I want to be able to log out of the app, so others cannot access my account information
10: settings page
As a user, I want to be able to change my settings, so I can decide my notifications and personal information
